<bibRefCitation author="Dana J. D." box="[380,515,1341,1363]" pageId="15" pageNumber="15" refId="ref51423" refString="Dana J. D. 1852. Crustacea, part I. United States Exploring Expedition during the years 1838 - 42 under the command of Ch. Wilkes U. S. N. 13: i- viii + 1 - 685. Philadelphia: C. Sherman." type="book" year="1852">Dana, 1852</bibRefCitation>
